      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRONTE LEE (8) can keep on winning after a head turning last start success, getting around the 320m at this track in 18.14. Has the ability and expected to go close again. SEVEN INN (1) has a strong overall record having 17 wins and 41 places from 85 starts but was out of the money last time when fifth (19.01) over 320m at this track. Solid record at the distance winning 10 races. Best form too dangerous to ignore. Have to include. SANDY BALE (3) is not the most reliable at box rise. Last start finished 4th in a Grade 5 on May 29 over 320m at this track behind All Things Go beaten 7 lengths (18.63). Suited here and expected to run well.",
